## Installation Commands (Copy-Paste Ready)

Run this in Termux to create the entire structure:

```bash
# Create base directory
mkdir -p ~/iot-data-shaper/{config,scripts,systemd,docs,logs}
cd ~/iot-data-shaper

# Save all scripts above to their respective paths
# Then make executable
chmod +x setup.sh config/*.sh scripts/*.sh systemd/*.sh

# Run setup
bash setup.sh